Name: Average resolution time of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' cases
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Vendor and the end of the case

Name: Total time spent in 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' before moving to 'Accepted + In Progress'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Average time difference between 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and 'Accepted + Wait - User'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Total duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' in cases leading to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Minimum time spent in 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' across all cases
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Vendor and the end of the case

Name: Average time from 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' to 'Completed + Resolved' compared to 'Accepted + Wait - User' to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Total time from 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' to the next activity in the most frequent variant
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Vendor and the end of the case

Name: Average time from 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' to 'Completed + Closed' in cases with 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Minimum resolution time of cases involving 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and ending with 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Average time from 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' to 'Completed + Closed', comparing cases with and without 'Accepted + Wait - User'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Total time from 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' to 'Completed + Resolved' in cases that also involve 'Accepted + Assigned'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Minimum time from 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' to the first occurrence of 'Completed + In Call' in any case
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' in cases that exceed the average case duration
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Vendor and the end of the case

Name: Total duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' in the top 5 longest process variants
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Vendor and the end of the case
